              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8394458691799770279">Andrew Williams spins a fascinating and complicated web in Arcadia’s Children: Samantha’s Revenge. Ex soldier Tarmy gets wrapped up in a plot that can destabilize the known galaxy if he doesn’t stop it. Williams’ world is vivid and unique, filled with strange creatures and interesting characters. If you love intrigue that goes with space operas like The Expanse, definitely check out Arcadia’s Children!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


