    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3055274164" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3055274164" />
    <a title="Pegboard" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/47722544-pegboard"><img alt="Pegboard" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1498516338p2/47722544.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3055274164?book_show_action=true">Dec 19, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Pegboard" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Pegboard" href="/user/show/47722544-pegboard">Pegboard</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3055274164" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14585164639795428426">I found Arcadia&apos;s Children: Samantha&apos;s Revenge a full-package science fiction. The fantasy and unusual conspiracies within the story makes this a suspense adventure that will keep the reader spellbound. Andrew R. Williams takes you to worlds unknown with technology that is only a dream in the author&apos;s mind. Claire Hyndman is would be my favorite character as she morphs into any character she wants. She adds a unique personality to the book. <br/><br/>Andrew R. Williams knows how to spin a story that will </span>
  <span id="freeText14585164639795428426" style="display:none">I found Arcadia's Children: Samantha's Revenge a full-package science fiction. The fantasy and unusual conspiracies within the story makes this a suspense adventure that will keep the reader spellbound. Andrew R. Williams takes you to worlds unknown with technology that is only a dream in the author's mind. Claire Hyndman is would be my favorite character as she morphs into any character she wants. She adds a unique personality to the book. <br /><br />Andrew R. Williams knows how to spin a story that will make you lose sight of your own world. For some reason I read Arcadia's Children: The Fyfield Plantation before Arcadia's Children: Samantha's Revenge. Each book can be read alone, but they are best read in order. The characters are rich, with bountiful personalities. I found Samantha's Revenge entreating from the beginning as a team escapes the clutches of Minton Mining Company. Science fiction fanatics will love this novel, and series. Be sure to set aside a block of time to finish this book since it is hard to put down. <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="14585164639795428426" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


