              <span id="reviewTextContainer3097832119" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5100092681054500872">This sci-fi fantasy story has many twists and turns throughout and grabbed my attention right from the beginning. Williams has poured so much imagination into it with phenomenal attention to detail. If you are looking to binge read for a few hours then this is definitely the novel for you, and from my perspective the only time I could put it down was when I finished it. I thoroughly enjoyed the read and have recommended it to all the bookworms I know. Great job.</span>

          </span>
